{"id":461,"date":"2020-12-08T02:43:00","date_gmt":"2020-12-08T02:43:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/casperwyomingtravelguide\/"},"modified":"2023-03-04T07:26:35","modified_gmt":"2023-03-04T07:26:35","slug":"casperwyomingtravelguide","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/casperwyomingtravelguide\/","title":{"rendered":"How To Spend A Weekend In Casper, Wyoming &#8211; And Stay Safe While Doing So."},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607394164355-AHU7C49BCZS4ZJKGEKRI\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" alt=\"casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607394164355-AHU7C49BCZS4ZJKGEKRI\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x3333\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5fcee36d7379aa3597692df2\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<blockquote>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">I was hosted by Visit Casper and all opinions are my own.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Welcome to Wyoming &#8211; Casper, Wyoming to be exact! This year I\u2019ve had the pleasure of visiting Wyoming <strong>TWICE. <\/strong>I first visited Yellowstone in Wyoming back in March and I recently returned for a trip to Casper. To be honest, I didn\u2019t know much about this region of the United States prior to my Yellowstone visit. I was pleasantly surprised on that first trip, so I knew I was in for a treat when<a href=\"https:\/\/visitcasper.com\"> Visit Casper<\/a> invited me to visit for a weekend.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">My first impression? <a href=\"https:\/\/visitcasper.com\">Casper is a relatively small town<\/a>(population: 57k) that reminded me a lot of West Texas. The city is in central Wyoming with a long history of oil and cowboy culture. If you were simply passing through, you might miss all that Casper has to offer. I can definitely say that it\u2019s a great weekend destination for eating your heart out, exploring the great outdoors, fly-fishing, and more.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">As my mom is on a mission to visit all 50 states, I brought her along for the journey and we were able to enjoy Casper in ways that we never imagined.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><em>As a very important note<\/em>, <a href=\"https:\/\/visitcasper.com\">Caspe<\/a>r is currently open for safe visitation. They are doing all that they can to protect both citizens and visitors. Masks are enforced, businesses offer outdoor seating, and many activities can be done while social-distancing.<\/p>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607394926315-IMY18GUQNJ5R9NB56N6G\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" alt=\"casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607394926315-IMY18GUQNJ5R9NB56N6G\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x3126\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5fcee66368c18617d403d702\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<h1 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\"><strong>WHERE TO STAY&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h1>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">While visiting Casper, I had the pleasure of staying at the <a href=\"https:\/\/ramkotacasper.com\/\">Ramkota Casper. <\/a> With a downtown location, this was the perfect launchpad for me to explore Casper. Every main attraction I visited was just minutes away, which made it easy to do as much as possible in a certain amount of time. My favorite aspects of staying at the Ramkota included:<\/p>\n<ul data-rte-list=\"default\">\n<li>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Free shuttle services to and from the airport<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Spacious rooms that allowed for complete relaxation with my mom<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Complimentary breakfast<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">As a note, masks are required. Measures are being taken to protect both employees and customers at the <a href=\" Ramkota Casper\">Ramkota Casper<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h1 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\"><strong>WHAT TO DO<\/strong><\/h1>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\"><strong>Go Fly Fishing <\/strong><\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 1213px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607394950501-HE6GCDVK7P92B4OBKYGL\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" alt=\"casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607394950501-HE6GCDVK7P92B4OBKYGL\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image-dimensions=\"1213x1516\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5fcee6858b174454e9910b87\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">People travel from all over the world to go fly fishing in Casper. With anywhere from 3000 to 5000 fish per mile, the area is one of the best big fish destinations in the USA. You\u2019ve gotta put this on your Casper bucket-list. You can take a guided tour with <a href=\"https:\/\/uglybugflyshop.crazyrainbow.net\/\">Ugly Bug Fly Shop<\/a> and learn everything from casting the rod to the process of tying a fly(bait used to lure the fish in). If you\u2019re anything like my mother and me, you might not catch a single fish. However, I can say that this is the most peaceful thing I\u2019ve done in a while. It certainly tested my patience. There\u2019s a first time for everything, right?<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\"><strong>Take The Scenic Route To Freemont Canyon <\/strong><\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607395001515-PM2T1H10IBRTF4OUTS4N\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" alt=\"casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607395001515-PM2T1H10IBRTF4OUTS4N\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x3125\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5fcee6af76f3eb1a46d568b1\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Drive out to Freemont Canyon to safely catch some of the best views in Natrona Country. You\u2019ll witness geological wonders from start to finish. If you\u2019re feeling really adventurous, you can kayak, boat, climb, or fish in the area.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\"><strong>Visit the Nicolaysen Art Museum <\/strong><\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607395034358-W1RCCIIZ0K7W9GO3ND7M\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" alt=\"casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607395034358-W1RCCIIZ0K7W9GO3ND7M\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x3334\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5fcee6d601eaf4591e1b9d6b\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">The<a href=\"https:\/\/thenic.org\/\"> Nicolaysen Art Museum<\/a> is a self-guided studio that features a collection of traditional and contemporary art. If you visit anytime soon, you must see <a href=\"https:\/\/thenic.org\/xg_portfolio\/georgia-rowswell-layer-fold-unfold\/\">Georgia Roswell\u2019s exhibit <\/a>which features Wyoming\u2019s landscape via discarded textiles. I\u2019ve never seen anything like it.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Note: You\u2019ll be required to social distance inside of the museum. Don\u2019t forget your mask!<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\"><strong>Chase Waterfalls at<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.visitcasper.com\/things-to-do\/outdoor-recreation\/hiking-trails\/rotary-park\/\"><strong> Rotary Park <\/strong><\/a><\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607395082621-3BE55JA12UO08XX8L4U7\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" alt=\"casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607395082621-3BE55JA12UO08XX8L4U7\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x3126\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5fcee7001a78ee5f01587a05\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.visitcasper.com\/things-to-do\/outdoor-recreation\/hiking-trails\/rotary-park\/\">Garden Creek falls<\/a> is a hidden gem at the base of Casper Mountain. You can safely hike the trails and stand at the base of the waterfall for gorgeous views.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\"><strong>Bring Out Your Inner Artist at <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/casperartguild.org\/\"><strong>Art 321<\/strong><\/a><\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 1242px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607395105598-5GM0EK7O7ML8XFOWEHL1\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" alt=\"casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607395105598-5GM0EK7O7ML8XFOWEHL1\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image-dimensions=\"1242x2208\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5fcee72001eaf4591e1bb21e\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Stop by this art organization to shop local art or get your creative juices flowing with an onsite art class! Choose from pottery, photography, painting, and more.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\"><strong>Shop For Souvenirs While Supporting Local Businesses <\/strong><\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \" data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"><\/p>\n<figure class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \" style=\"max-width: 2500px;\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"image-block-wrapper\" data-animation-role=\"image\">\n<div class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n\n              has-aspect-ratio\n            \"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607395150492-P3AMHJO7FMRD3YOCV01E\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" alt=\"casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image=\"https:\/\/images.squarespace-cdn.com\/content\/v1\/57a43cf715d5db0bee1397d9\/1607395150492-P3AMHJO7FMRD3YOCV01E\/casperwyomingtravelguide\" data-image-dimensions=\"2500x3333\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5fcee74a509e863c6822675b\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">In downtown Casper, you\u2019ll find a local shop at every turn! For reference, you can carry a piece of Casper with you by shopping at <a href=\"https:\/\/floralrhino.com\/\">Floral Rhino<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.loutaubert.com\/\">Lou Taubert Ranch Outfitters<\/a>, or<a href=\"https:\/\/wyomade.com\/\"> WyoMade Apparel &amp; Craft goods<\/a> before you go!<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><em>Masks will be enforced inside local businesses. <\/em><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left;\"><strong>WHERE TO EAT AND DRINK<\/strong><\/h2>\n<div class=\"\n  sqs-gallery-container\n  sqs-gallery-block-slider\n\n  sqs-gallery-has-controls\n\n  sqs-gallery-block-show-meta\n\n  block-animation-none\n  clear\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"sqs-gallery\">\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/DD14AE36-9A8C-4335-A22A-F0F15182EA19.jpg\" alt=\"DD14AE36-9A8C-4335-A22A-F0F15182EA19.JPG\" data-image=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/DD14AE36-9A8C-4335-A22A-F0F15182EA19.jpg\" data-image-dimensions=\"1242x2208\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5fcee446b8233e30df9c996a\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/2E5323F0-7DE2-434C-A04E-6EEC32525FBD.jpg\" alt=\"2E5323F0-7DE2-434C-A04E-6EEC32525FBD.JPG\" data-image=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/2E5323F0-7DE2-434C-A04E-6EEC32525FBD.jpg\" data-image-dimensions=\"1242x2208\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5fcee44b1a78ee5f01580c3f\" data-type=\"image\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https:\/\/heyciara.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/3A3497F6-9740-44C6-9583-97089088E1852.jpg\" alt=\"3A3497F6-9740-44C6-9583-97089088E1